00133             if(&desc!=this) {
00134                 m_counter = desc.m_counter;
00135                 for(UINT i=0; i<m_counter; i++) {
00136                     m_desc[i] = desc.m_desc[i];
00137                 }
00138             }
00139             return *this;
00140         }
00141 
00143         BOOLEAN AppendMePhonebookDescriptor(const MePhonebookDescriptor & desc) {
00144             if(m_counter<c_max_phonebook_descriptors-1) {
00145                 m_desc[m_counter] = desc;
00146                 m_counter++;
00147                 return TRUE;
00148             }
00149             return FALSE;
00150         }
00152         const MePhonebookDescriptor & Get(INT idx) const {
00153             ASSERT_DEBUG(idx<c_max_phonebook_descriptors);
00154             return m_desc[m_counter];
00155         }
00157         UINT GetCount() const { return m_counter; }
00158 
00159     private:
00160         MePhonebookDescriptor m_desc[c_max_phonebook_descriptors];
00161         UINT m_counter;

00173 class AtGenericCmdType {
00174 
00175     public:
00176 
00177         AtGenericCmdType() : m_length(0), m_data_ptr(0) { ; }
00178 
00179         AtGenericCmdType(const AtGenericCmdType & cmd) : m_length(0), m_data_ptr(0) { 
00180             if (cmd.m_length > 0) {
00181                 m_data_ptr = new UINT8[cmd.m_length]; 
00182                 if(m_data_ptr != 0) {
00183                     m_length = cmd.m_length; 
00184                     memcpy(m_data_ptr, cmd.m_data_ptr, m_length);
00185                 }
00186             }
00187         }
00188         
00189         ~AtGenericCmdType() { 
00190             m_length = 0; 
00191             delete[] m_data_ptr;
00192             m_data_ptr = 0;
00193         }
00194 
00195         void Push(INT length, const UINT8 * data_ptr) {
00196             m_data_ptr = (length > 0) ? new UINT8[length] : 0;
00197             if (m_data_ptr != 0) {
00198                 m_length = length;
00199                 memcpy(m_data_ptr, data_ptr, length);
00200             }
00201         }
00202 
00203         INT     m_length;
00204         UINT8 * m_data_ptr;
00205 };
